questionResult_name: Are You Ready To Get Married

answersResultList.title: You're not quite ready to get married.
answersResultList.resultContent: Your relationship is awesome, except when it sucks. You could do worse, but maybe you could do better. You feel claustrophobic when there isn't much action. You're probably on the right path, but the next rough patch could be a deal-breaker. If your wedding happened today, you'd say, ''I might,'' not ''I do.'' Better put this on hold for now.
